{"tid":413142,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林峯廣州世界巡迴演唱會晒新紋身","createTime":"2017-09-25T09:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T14:52:35.000Z","uid":14730,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6543408a696dce3e7025baf81a14d5f72a197f0","tid":413142,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/170433_57a523a95fe35a714b5ac7c460eb915f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F170433_57a523a95fe35a714b5ac7c460eb915f.jpg&h=7ba0d2d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以廣州為首站的林峯《Heart Attack》世界巡迴演唱會於9月23日圓滿結束，全場爆滿。林峯不停勁舞騷肌，將全場的氣氛炒至最高點。其中一幕撕衫環節，露出他苦練多時的結實肌肉之餘，遍佈全身的紋身更是相當吸睛，令所有女歌迷熱血沸騰。原來紋身只是暫時畫上身作表演之用，並非真紋。紋身的像真度相當高，遍佈前胸、手臂及背部，心藏位置更有一個像示意「爆炸」的圖案，十分型格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2y30qiC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2y30qiC&d=07lbfwDk5yoNSV6O8FIOT49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=140d2b93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2y30qiC</a>"},{"pid":"144ba79e664f0075bcacb6a49425ec97c8c47817","tid":413142,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"比卡超呢"},{"pid":"0f3211d28039b66b55a2ca56c7d70dd9cc840314","tid":413142,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"紋係個乳度<br />\n<br />\n即係爆乳<br />\n<br />\n有爆鳩吳千語之意"}]}